WEBVTT

00:06.107 --> 00:07.377
Dear Lord...

00:09.009 --> 00:10.609
please forgive me.

00:11.912 --> 00:13.352
I was a fool.

00:15.183 --> 00:17.250
I thought You'd betrayed me,

00:17.251 --> 00:19.791
and all I could hear
was my own anger.

00:22.223 --> 00:23.763
But now I know.

00:25.893 --> 00:27.563
You have chosen me.

00:28.896 --> 00:31.066
You have a purpose for me.

00:35.469 --> 00:38.738
You said to Jeremiah,
"Call to Me,

00:38.739 --> 00:40.069
"and I will answer you,

00:40.074 --> 00:42.814
"and I will tell you
great and mighty things

00:42.815 --> 00:44.810
which you do not know."

00:47.681 --> 00:49.281
Well, here I am, God...

00:50.218 --> 00:52.818
calling to You.

00:52.820 --> 00:54.620
I am Your servant.

00:55.989 --> 00:58.325
Reveal my path to me,

00:58.326 --> 01:01.496
and I shall do
everything You demand.

01:06.967 --> 01:08.667
Your will be done.

